description: The Superchief Ordinals Genesis Pass is a unique NFT collection on the BTC blockchain. As the inaugural release, these 200 passes are just the beginning, paving the way for a full collection of 1500 set to be released in subsequent drops. This first-of-its-kind Utility Genesis Pass by Superchief Gallery NFT, the 1st IRL NFT Gallery In The World, gives holders unparalleled access to Superchief's multichain community and AL spots to upcoming ordinal / “artwork on Bitcoin” releases. Beyond the digital, holders receive exclusive invites to international Superchief events and benefit from special holder-only airdrops. It's the nexus of art, bitcoin, and exclusive IRL perks.
name: Superchief Ordinals Genesis
